        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are in Gorilla Stance.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You pound your chest before slamming into your foes.</p>\n<p>Attempt an Intimidation check to <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.actionspf2e\" data-id=\"2u915NdUyQan6uKF\" draggable=\"true\"> Demoralize</a>, then make one gorilla slam <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.actionspf2e\" data-id=\"VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR\" draggable=\"true\"> Strike</a> against the same target. If your Strike hits, you gain a circumstance bonus to the damage roll equal to triple the value of the target's <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.conditionitems\" data-id=\"TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-book-open\"></i> Frightened</a> condition.</p>\n<p><strong>Special</strong> If you have this feat, while you are in Gorilla Stance, you gain a <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.actionspf2e\" data-id=\"pprgrYQ1QnIDGZiy\" draggable=\"true\"> Climb</a> Speed of 15 feet.</p>"
